    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a dependable ride that's perfect for getting you where you need to go! This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some authentic character and signs of its busy life on the road. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that\u2019s ready to continue its journey with a new owner who appreciates a great value!",
