    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great fit for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few stains, though the cabin remains functional. While the car runs and drives, it will likely require some mechanical attention and routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a project car or a parts donor. While the engine does start, it suffers from several persistent issues, including significant oil leaks and a rough idle that suggests internal wear. The body shows signs of neglect with visible rust on the lower panels and several dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn and some electrical components, such as the power windows, are non-functional. It is drivable for short distances, but a full mechanical inspection and major repairs are necessary for it to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 4000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "$33,500 - 2018 sedan in good condition. The exterior has minor paint chips and light surface scratches. The interior is clean with minimal wear on the upholstery. All mechanical systems, including the engine and transmission, are in working order.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
